headline.main: After Bombs, Pakistan Tightens Security for Rare Major Cricket Match
headline.print_headline: After Bombs, Pakistan Tightens Security for Rare Major Cricket Match

lead_paragraph: Vanderbilt did what no other member of the Southeastern Conference could do this season. The Commodores swept Florida, and that could be enough to almost guarantee an at-large bid to the NCAA Tournament.
